description.narrative: The objectives of the Project are: (i) to enhance adaptation to climate risks, (ii) to improve agricultural productivity among the Targeted Communities and (iii) in the event of an Eligible Crisis or Emergency, to provide immediate and effective response to said Eligible Crisis or Emergency.
